Text.string: What'd you get into last night?
A fine night for a Vault Hunter!
The town of Reliance got its name after every man and woman took turns defending it during the settlin' days. Even the little ones.
I think swamp chic might catch on. It's a fashion statement AND a lifestyle!
I make my own deodorant out of swamp algae. Wanna try some?
You don't know the meanin' of “muggy” till you spend a summer on Eden-6.
There's always been a rumor of a Vault on Eden-6, but Typhon DeLeon himself couldn't even find it!
If I could sum up swamp life in one word, it'd probably be... “moist”.
They call the Eden system the paradise planets. If you're a saurian, maybe.
There're three types of swamp ass. Regular. Supreme. And “I itched my bunghole straight off my turd shoot.”
Guess Eden-6 ain't SO bad. Except for the saurians. And the jabbers. And the swamp ass.
You might be asking yourself why a planet owned by a major corporation barely got basic plumbing... Beats me.
My pa was in logging. Grandma—yup, logging. Grandpa was a quilter. It's a thing.
Eden-6 may look like a backwater swamp of hellish rot, but... I don't know how to finish that sentence.
Saurians are good eatin'! If they don't eat you first, that is.
Ever been to a maw-fish bake? That's a party right there.
Yeah, it's a pretty cool ship I guess, but it ain't no dank shack, that's for sure.
I'll say one thing for being on this ship: no swamp ass. Feels sorta unnatural after all those years on Eden-6.
This ship is like a floatin' palace. Fancy!
I'll tell you what I DON'T miss: angry saurians. At least we're safe from them big ol' bastards on this here ship.
Maybe I should sell some swamp clothes up here on the Sanctuary. I think they might catch on.
Was it something I said, or the smell?
That's the end of the end, I guess.
That's what I should've said! Mud britches, bitches!
Why won't anyone pay attention to me?
A jabber stole my wallet once. And my heart!
Must have been something I ate.
What's that smell? Is that me?
I'm hungry. Just wanted ya to know that.
I don't care what anyone says. Swamp folk are good folk.
I could go for a game of frolf right about now.
[burp] Catch that one and paint it blue.
You don't even know my name, do ya?
Ain't you the cock of the walk?
